data.description: Beautifully remodeled 3 bedroom - 2 bath, Florida Ranch-style home which shows like a model!  This a perfect family home or amazing rental property.  The entire home has been fully remodeled from floor to ceiling.  Conveniently located close to McGregor, US41, and Colonial Blvd, tucked away in the quiet Colonial Terrace neighborhood. 10 minutes to I-75, 8 minutes to downtown Ft. Myers, and 5 minutes across the bridge to Cape Coral. The Chefs kitchen will impress you with new white shaker cabinets, upgraded quartz counters, breakfast bar, newer stainless appliances, with generous storage space.  Both bathrooms are completely custom bringing a luxury feel, equipped with higher-end tile work.  Large Florida room can be set up as a 4th bedroom if needed.  Great fenced in backyard and is spacious enough to build a pool. This beautifully remodeled home with many upgrades will wow you!  Newer roof, new AC, freshly painted inside and out. Minutes away from grocery stores, beaches, restaurants, shopping centers, etc.  Make your Move!
